---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AgentAnchor" description="B2B platform for AI agent trust and compliance - Enterprise governance dashboard">
  <article class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
          </svg>
          Back to Projects
        </a>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-vorion-500/20 to-accent-cyan/20 border border-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-3xl">
            ‚öì
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">AgentAnchor</h1>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/30 flex items-center gap-1">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                Live
              </span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 border border-amber-500/30">
                README Available
              </span>
              <span class="text-sm text-slate-500">Proprietary</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          B2B enterprise platform for AI agent governance. Manage agent trust, monitor behavior,
          enforce compliance policies, and maintain audit trails across your organization.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
        <a
          href="https://app.agentanchorai.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500 hover:bg-vorion-600 text-white transition-colors"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
          </svg>
          Open AgentAnchor
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://agentanchorai.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white transition-colors"
        >
          Marketing Site
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Notice -->
      <div class="mb-12 p-6 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-400 mb-1">Proprietary Software</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-200/70">
              AgentAnchor is commercial software. This page provides detailed documentation
              about functionality and architecture for transparency. The underlying SDK packages
              used by AgentAnchor are open source.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Overview -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            AgentAnchor is the enterprise-facing platform of the Vorion ecosystem. It provides
            organizations with a centralized dashboard to manage, monitor, and govern their
            AI agent deployments. Built on the open BASIS standard and ATSF framework.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            The platform enables compliance teams, security officers, and AI operations managers
            to maintain oversight of autonomous systems without impeding their productivity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Features -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Key Features</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üìä
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Trust Dashboard</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Real-time visualization of agent trust scores across your organization.
              Filter by team, project, or trust tier. Identify at-risk agents before issues occur.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üîí
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Policy Enforcement</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Define and enforce governance policies at organization, team, and agent levels.
              Automatic policy evaluation via Cognigate integration.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üë•
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Human-in-the-Loop</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Review and approve high-risk agent actions. Escalation workflows route
              decisions to appropriate stakeholders based on severity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üìú
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Audit Trails</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Complete audit trail of all agent actions, decisions, and trust changes.
              Exportable reports for compliance and regulatory requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üîî
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Alerting</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Configurable alerts for trust score drops, policy violations, and
              escalation timeouts. Integrates with Slack, PagerDuty, and webhooks.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-vorion-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-4">
              üè¢
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Multi-Tenant</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
              Enterprise multi-tenancy with team isolation, SSO integration, and
              role-based access control. SOC 2 Type II compliant infrastructure.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Architecture -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Architecture</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
          AgentAnchor is built on open source foundations:
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                OS
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-white">@vorionsys/atsf-core</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Trust engine, behavioral scoring, decay algorithms</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                OS
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-white">@vorion/agent-sdk</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Agent connection, task management, approval workflows</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                OS
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-white">@vorion/a3i</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Authorization hooks, execution tracking, orchestration</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400 text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                P
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-white">AgentAnchor Web</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Next.js dashboard, API layer, authentication (Proprietary)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Pricing -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Pricing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">
          AgentAnchor offers flexible pricing for organizations of all sizes.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Starter</h3>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Free</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Up to 5 agents, basic dashboard</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-vorion-500/10 border border-vorion-500/30">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-vorion-400 mb-2">Team</h3>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">$99/mo</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Up to 50 agents, full features</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-white mb-2">Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Custom</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Unlimited agents, SSO, SLA</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Related Projects</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/projects/aurais" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Aurais Assistant
          </a>
          <a href="/projects/basis" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            BASIS Standard
          </a>
          <a href="/packages#agent-sdk" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">
            @vorion/agent-sdk
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
